// â€¢ Updated alert JSON to match oanda_bridge.py expected keys.
// â€¢ Replaced "timestamp" â†’ "alert_id" (unix via timenow).
// â€¢ Replaced "risk_pips" â†’ "risk_pct":1.0.
// â€¢ Maintained identical logic, alerts, and structure.
